{"product_id":"madara-sebum-control-clear-skin-wash-140ml","title":"MÁDARA Sebum Control Clear Skin Wash 140ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eFree from harsh surfactants, this plant-based cleanser purifies acne-prone skin, helping to minimize the appearance of blackheads and blemishes. Fermented polyaccharides help to regulate sebum and balance the microbiome for a healthy-looking skin. Juniper stem cells and extracts of lichen and mate deliver soothing and antioxidant benefits. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to damp skin, rinse off. Follow with a moisturiser. Use in combination with other ACNE formulas for the best results.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Coco-glucoside, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Xanthan Gum, Propanediol, Sodium PCA, Sodium levulinate, Lactic Acid, Ilex Paraguariensis (Mate) Leaf Extract, Aroma, Acacia Senegal Gum, Alcohol, Sodium anisate, CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), Rhamnose, Cetraria Islandica (Iceland Moss) Extract, Usnea Barbata (Lichen) Extract, Juniperus Communis (Juniper) Callus Culture Extract, Glucose, Glucuronic Acid, Linalool\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49887907905863,"sku":null,"price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-sebum-control-clear-skin-wash-140ml-429167.jpg?v=1739897250","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-sebum-control-clear-skin-wash-140ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}